CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 1. Headline reads: "First Baptist Church, Penn Township, Is Scene Of Ceremony Uniting Miss Gaines, Mr. Hollinger"
TitMainTitle: Groom Leonard Claybert Hollinger, and bride Arlene Allen Gaines Hollinger wearing satin wedding gown with sweetheart neckline and lace trimmed veil, posed behind four tiered wedding cake, for reception, possibly in Lincoln Park Junior High School
